Here's a one-liner that stops the AnimatedMove function moving the
cursor.  Animated menus are not affected.  

*** move.c.orig Tue Jul  7 14:54:15 1998
--- move.c      Tue Jul  7 14:54:20 1998
***************
*** 170,176 ****
          XMapWindow(dpy,tmp_win->icon_w);
          if (fAnimated) {
            AnimatedMoveOfWindow(tmp_win->icon_pixmap_w, -1,-1,
!                               
tmp_win->icon_x_loc,FinalY,TRUE,-1,NULL);
          } else {
            XMoveWindow(dpy, tmp_win->icon_pixmap_w,
tmp_win->icon_x_loc,FinalY);
          }
