Scwm was originally derived from fvwm2 code, and thus already provides
a superset of fvwm's interface possibilities. I think the greatest
benefit would be combining fvwm's name recognition and large user base
with scwm's flexibility.

> A window-manager that merged scwm's guts with fvwm2's glory would be ideal.

