brian moore <bem@cmc.net>:
> You think it's "peevish" to not want to follow the direction of the
> current maintainer of code?  Perhaps you should add that wisdom to your
> essays.  "People who don't like the way code is going dare not try to
> take it in a different direction."  It will show a whole new side of
